## 🧠 A Word from the Developer

As we all know, *Helldivers II* has this exclusive mini-game—  
Only accessible if you bought the **Super Citizen Edition**, played on the Super Destroyer:  
**Stratagem Hero**.

Not long ago, I got super into "Defending Super Earth,"  
and meanwhile, we were learning Android development at school.  

So I thought—why not try recreating the mini-game as a mobile app?

Just imagine: like a true Helldiver, inputting stratagems via touchscreen.  
It actually sounds... kinda fun.

To be honest, this project’s a bit of a mess.  
The code is... tragic.  
From a small mountain of spaghetti to a big one.

So hey, treat it as a small, silly toy—don’t expect too much. 😉

> If you happen to enjoy it, maybe consider donating a cup of bubble tea ☕ as motivation!

